{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- he was-- yeah, he was here twice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I brought him here twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Last time I brought him was for my granddaughter's bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when I made my, my, my bar mitzvah, so I brought him up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in '47, we couldn't-- it was getting itchy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when are we going to get out of Germany?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Got to leave Germany, new [INAUDIBLE] state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Obviously, everybody wanted to go to America, United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't look that we have anybody that would be able to do that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You, you had an aunt here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She couldn't help you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow, I really don't-- either, either they weren't willing-- I really don't want to, you know, say anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's not alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May she rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow, we didn't get any papers to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no-- didn't look like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we-- sooner or later, after Israel, I guess everybody knows you're going to wind up in Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when the Canadian Jewish congress came out that you can-- they would pick everybody up, anybody under 18 with no parents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So it was again in Europe, they have papers, very easy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it was just to get out, you know, get, get out of Germany, get out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And got my paper, that I was, you know [INAUDIBLE], and I went, and I went to Canada.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By myself, in, in June of '47.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it's a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I have some of the pictures, too, that I'll show you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We really had a boat full of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say a couple thousand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody under 18.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to be under 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a guide.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
